acceptance_criteria: "- README contains minimal package summary, install commands, and links.\\n- docs/README.md provides a short agent path.\\n- docs/usage.md contains CLI, extension, options, and TypeScript API details.\\n- docs/release.md contains release workflow, GitHub checks, npm checks, and versioning.\\n- docs/development.md contains layout, TypeScript policy, pm governance, temp install, and secret review guidance.\\n- package.json pm docs metadata and npm files include docs/."
