resolution: Moved detailed package documentation into docs/ and reduced README to minimal install/run/docs links.
expected_result: "The top-level README stays minimal while docs pages carry detailed usage, release, and development guidance linked for agent progressive disclosure."
actual_result: "README.md is now minimal; docs/README.md, docs/usage.md, docs/release.md, and docs/development.md contain the detailed progressive-disclosure documentation; package.json includes docs/ in npm files and pm docs metadata; npm pack --dry-run included all docs files."
